Default value: <p>NILU</p>
</p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='area' href='#area'></a> area</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Exclusive)</span><span class='description'><p>Name of an area to get sensor stations from. See available areas below.</p>
